						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle"><b>Quote:</b></div><div class="quotecontent">Also, i usually don't worry about real physics, I set the values to what looks and feels best for a game. Real physics aren't fun in a platformer. Don't you hate games where you can't change your direction in the middle of a jump?</div>
