						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">Disch wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent"><br />1) What purpose do those 'INX' lines serve?  Are they really doing what you expect them to?<br />2) When do you want that BNE to branch?  and when do you want it NOT to branch?  Is it really branching how you'd expect?<br />3) How are you keeping track of which number you are currently displaying?  And how do you know which number to display next?<br />4) How many times is this code <em>actually</em> writing to the sprite DMA register ($4014) per frame?  How many times do you want it to write to sprite DMA?<br /><br /></div>
